text: Jolien Maliga Boumkwo (born 27 August 1993 in Ghent) is a Belgian athlete competing in the shot put and hammer throw. She hold national records in both events. ==International competitions== {| |- !colspan="6"|Representing |- |2011 |European Junior Championships |Tallinn, Estonia |13th (q) |Shot put |14.32 m |- |2012 |World Junior Championships |Barcelona, Spain |10th |Shot put |15.31 m |- |2013 |European U23 Championships |Tampere, Finland |14th (q) |Shot put |15.21 m |- |rowspan=2|2015 |rowspan=2|European U23 Championships |rowspan=2|Tallinn, Estonia |6th |Shot put |16.47 m |- |14th (q) |Hammer throw |63.24 m |- |2016 |European Championships |Amsterdam, Netherlands |14th (q) |Shot put |16.66 m |} ==Personal bests== Outdoor *Shot put – 17.09 (Brussels 2016) NR *Discus throw – 50.60 (Kessel-Lo 2014) *Hammer throw – 67.30 (Brussels 2016) NR Indoor *Shot put – 15.81 (Ghent 2016) ==References== *All- Athletics profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female shot putters Category:Belgian female hammer throwers Category:Sportspeople from Ghent
